article_id:643,category_name:News,title_name:Gift for Issues in Version 1.10.0,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed that the following issues occur in version 1.10.0, which was released <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564380000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・An Issue Regarding Mercurial Gauntlet</div><div><br></div><div>・Issue Regarding Afflictions</div><div><br></div><div>See each notification for details about these issues.</div><div><br></div><div>To thank you for your patience, we will be giving the following gift to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564462800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Wyrmite x500</div><div><br></div><div>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after logging in. If the gift isn&rsquo;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1564462800,update_time1564462526